/ Stage 5 — the developer's escape hatch for a type-unknown value.
/ `as object/json` stamps the cast (shape `object`, encoding `json`);
/ navigation then materialises through the (object, json) reader and the
/ field resolves. Companion to NavigationOnTypeUnknown_AsksForAsType:
/ that one errors, this one shows the fix. Architect 829785fbe — json
/ values are `object`-shaped, not `text`.
- set %x% = "{\"port\":8080}" as object/json
- assert %x.port% equals 8080
